The BRA/04/045 (BIO.COM) aims to:
 1) Develop a strategy for marketing of sustainable use of biodiversity in Brazil;
 2) Support and facilitate the marketing of products for the sustainable use of biodiversity in Brazil;
 3) Establish and strengthen contacts between producers and marketing channels;
 4) To guide and empower producers, contributing to the achievement of necessary adjustments of the products to market;
 5) To monitor, evaluate and disseminate marketing experiences.
